title.en: Henkyou no Binbou Hakushaku ni Totsugu Koto ni natta no de Ryouchi Kaikaku ni Hagemimasu
"Omae ga Kawari ni Shine" to Iwareta Watashi. Imouto no Migawari ni Reikoku na Henkyou Haku no Moto e Totsugi, Shiawase wo Teniireru
Narikin Reijou no Shiawase na Kekkon ~Kane no Mouja to Nonoshirareta Reijou wa Chichioya ni Urarete Henkyou no Buta Koushaku to Shiawase ni naru~
Ikenie to shite Surerareta no de, Henkyou Hakke ni Jibun wo Urimasu
Shoudoubutsu-kei Reijou wa Koori no Ouji ni Dekiai Sareru
Kon'yaku Haki 23-kai no Reiketsu Kikoushi wa Inaka no Ponkotsu Reijou ni Furimawasareru
The Count Chose an Unladylike Lady
Konyaku Haki no Akui wa Shoukan Kara Okaeshi Shimasu
Imouto ni Konyakusha wo Toraretara Mishiranu Koushaku-sama ni Kyuukonsaremashita
Onna Hakushaku Amber ni wa Shousai ga aru! - Yatto Jiyuu ni Nareta no de, Saikon Nante Okotowari
Moto Konyakusha kara Nigeru Tame Kyuuketsu Hakushaku ni Koibito no Furi wo Onegai shitara, Naze ka Dekiai Mode ni narimashita
Suterare Hanayome no Saikon - Koori no Henkyou Haku wa Saiai o Chikau
Akuyaku Reijou wa Mou Zenbu ga Iya ni Natta no de, Kioku Soushitsu no Furi wo suru Koto ni shita
Zense Watashi ni Kyoumi ga Nakatta Otto, Chara Hen shite Dekiai shite Kite mo Taiou ni Komarimasu!
